    <item>
      <title>[부음] 김정숙씨 별세 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2026/02/25/YBG4NDHX3NBWFLGTEUNVU7E5JQ/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2026/02/25/YBG4NDHX3NBWFLGTEUNVU7E5JQ/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
